---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — CalcTax"
  description="How CalcTax earns revenue through affiliate partnerships while keeping all calculators free."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <p>
      CalcTax.ca is a free tax calculator website. To keep our tools free and
      ad-free, we earn revenue through affiliate partnerships.
    </p>

    <h2>What This Means</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this Site are affiliate links. When you click an affiliate
      link and sign up for a product or service, the company pays us a referral
      commission. <strong>This comes at no extra cost to you</strong> — the price
      you pay is the same whether you use our link or go directly to the site.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Choose What to Recommend</h2>
    <p>
      We only recommend products we believe are genuinely useful for Canadians
      filing their taxes. Our recommendations are based on product quality,
      relevance to the calculator you're using, and value to the user — not on
      which company pays the highest commission.
    </p>
    <p>
      Affiliate partnerships <strong>never influence calculator results</strong>.
      Your tax calculations are based solely on CRA-published rates and the
      information you provide.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Current Partners</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Wealthsimple Tax</strong> — Free tax filing software for Canadians. We may receive a commission when you file through our link.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to Identify Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate links on this Site are marked with "File Free" call-to-action
      buttons that appear after your calculator results. Links to external
      products open in a new tab and are tagged with <code>rel="sponsored"</code>
      in the page source.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about our affiliate relationships, contact us at
      <a href="/contact">our contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
